  "title": "Accountant (6 months contract / Woodlands) - SS10",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Accountant (6 months contract)</strong></h2><ul><li>Location: Woodlands</li><li>Working Timing : Monday - Thursday 8.30am - 6pm. Friday 8.30am - 5.30am</li><li>Salary : $4300 to $5000 (subject to qualifications and experience)</li></ul><h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Post and review journal entries in NetSuite</p></li><li><p>Perform month-end closing and balance sheet reconciliations</p></li><li><p>Maintain fixed asset register and run depreciation</p></li><li><p>Prepare management reports, variance analysis, and forecasts</p></li><li><p>Support grant and restricted fund tracking</p></li><li><p>Assist in reports for government agencies, donors, and grantors</p></li><li><p>Prepare audit schedules (PBCs) and support audit queries</p></li><li><p>Prepare GST F5 returns</p></li><li><p>Review AR/AP journals and verify payment, refund, and e-claims batches</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Degree in Accounting or Finance</p></li><li><p>ACCA / CPA preferred</p></li><li><p>2–5 years accounting experience</p></li><li><p>Experience in non-profit, social services, or service-based organisations preferred</p></li><li><p>Experience with NetSuite or similar ERP systems</p></li><li><p>Proficient in MS Excel (e.g. pivot tables, lookups)<br /></p><p>Samuel Siaw</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd</p><p>EA No: 14C7279</p><p>Reg No: R2412474</p><p></p></li></ul>",
